items.name: Password-Policy-Validator
items.description: The goal of this project is to analyze the dataset and verify whether the passwords comply with the company’s security policies. To achieve this, we added a new column indicating whether each password meets the compliance rules. Passwords that satisfy all requirements are labeled as strong, while those that do not are labeled as weak.
